This repository contains the working draft of the Cover Art Specification. Open
issues that still need to be resolved can be found at
https://github.com/ocharles/CAA-spec/issues.

You are encouraged to fork this repository and make ammendments. When you are
happy with ammendments, send a pull request and people can discuss whether or
not they agree with your ammendments. Then, we can do like congress and have
ammendment of the ammendment of the ammendment.
